               <p>CHARLES JOHN MARE. I was opposite <placeName id="t18340703-98-crimeloc545">Foster-lane, Cheapside</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18340703-98-crimeloc545" type="placeName" value="Foster-lane, Cheapside"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18340703-98-crimeloc545" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340703-98-off543 t18340703-98-crimeloc545"></join>, on the 19th of June, between two and three o'clock - I felt some one touch me behind - I turned, and saw the prisoner putting my handkerchief into his bosom, and running over the way - I ran after him down Foster-lane - I saw him throw my handkerchief down - I took it up.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340703-98-person631">
